<list><item>Residence of Julian at Antioch</item> <item>His successful Expedition against the Persians</item> <item>Passage of the Tigris</item> <item>The Retreat and Death of Julian</item> <item>Election of Jovian</item> <item>He saves the Roman Army by a disgraceful Treaty</item></list>



